*&quot;Norfolk&quot; (CA-137) was a heavy cruiser laid down in December 1944 at the Philadelphia Naval Shipyard, but construction was cancelled in August 1945
* was a destroyer leader/frigate in service from 1953 to 1970
* is a commissioned in 1983 and decommissioned in 2014.
* a planned attack submarine

